&ldquo;Why me?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your lighthouse eyes&rdquo;
&ldquo;I was seeing red&rdquo;
&ldquo;You were in the midnight sunset&rdquo;
&ldquo;No, it had already set&rdquo;
&ldquo;No, it was golden-red&rdquo;
&ldquo;It was ripe but raw&rdquo;
&ldquo;And the sky must&rsquo;ve bled&rdquo;

